include $(TOPDIR)target.mk
CURDIR:=$(shell echo $(PWD))$(DIRSEP)
SRCDIR:=$(TOPDIR)src
OBJDIR:=$(TOPDIR)obj
BINDIR:=$(TOPDIR)bin
TARGET_BINDIR:=$(BINDIR)/$(TARGET_DIR)
TARGET_OBJDIR:=$(OBJDIR)/$(TARGET_DIR)
T:=$(TOPDIR)/targets
B:=$(TARGET_BINDIR)/$(DBG)
O:=$(TARGET_OBJDIR)/$(DBG)
OBJ_DIRECTORIES:=$(OBJDIR) $(TARGET_OBJDIR)
OUT_DIRECTORIES:=$(BINDIR) $(TARGET_BINDIR)
ALL_DIRECTORIES:=$(OBJ_DIRECTORIES) $(OUT_DIRECTORIES)
INCLUDES:=$(FI)"$(CC_INC)" $(FI)"$(SRCDIR)"
OUT_LIBS:=$(FL)"$(CC_LIB)" $(FL)"$(B)"
OBJ_LIBS:=$(FL)"$(CC_LIB)" $(FL)"$(O)"
HEADERS:=$(wildcard $(SRCDIR)/*.h)
SOURCES:=$(wildcard $(SRCDIR)/*.c)
OBJECTS:=$(patsubst $(SRCDIR)/%.c,$(O)%.o,$(SOURCES))
COMPILE_BIN:=$(CC) $(OUT_LIBS) $(Fc) $(OBJECTS) $(Fo) $(B)
COMPILE_OBJ:=$(CC) $(OBJ_LIBS)